1f97841f50396a","tid":40672,"uid":105352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b19ab0cddccb7bc704314481c3a4be356e23bf69","tid":40672,"uid":58403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T08:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到咁快個故已經有6年.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得係舊登時為左呢個故而申請ac<br />\n<br />\n完故之後勁唔捨得, 仲同走青巴拎左聯絡方法, 大家隔住電腦捉膝長談左好耐好耐<br />\n<br />\n之後走青巴突然潛水三年, 又突然出現返<br />\n<br />\n見到佢有機會同欣姐再續租, 個心都好安慰<br />\n<br />\n可惜三年前唔知佢上返水, 知道佢有後續故事既時候佢已經又深潛左, 冇機會同佢講聲加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好掛住佢, 好想知佢同欣姐而家點樣, 巴絲打不如一齊推呢個post 推到佢上水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知走青巴打有冇上連登<br />\n<br />\nBTW 啊紫個結局真係好諷刺，始終都係佢爸爸認可<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f95962da5e7b4ac28a2a81bd3579a08fbbb05ab","tid":40672,"uid":105352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T19:09:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5592772243442140fef2fe8655af4443b9e38e7c","tid":40672,"uid":105352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90478937bbb27cafadf27d93ba48dccf76823adb","tid":40672,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e70da07476bc38ac85948c47a19fc06f6f5b074","tid":40672,"uid":35331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}